<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Information | SendMate</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <% if (!user) { %>
            <%- include('partials/nav') %> <!-- Nav for logged-in users -->
                <% } else { %>
                    <%- include('partials/nav_users') %> <!-- Nav for guests -->
                        <% } %>

                            <main class="py-10 mt-10">
                                <div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 flex flex-col space-y-8">

                                    <!-- Step 1: Registration -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 1: Registration</h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>Visit Homepage:</b> Click on the "Sign Up" button.</li>
                                            <li><b>Fill in Your Details:</b> Enter your Username, Email, and Password.
                                            </li>
                                            <li><b>Confirm Registration:</b> Check your email for a confirmation link
                                                and click it to activate your account.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Step 2: Login -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 2: Login</h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>Go to the Login Page:</b> Click on the "Login" button on the
                                                homepage.</li>
                                            <li><b>Enter Your Credentials:</b> Input your registered email and password.
                                            </li>
                                            <li><b>Access Your Dashboard:</b> Once logged in, you'll be directed to your
                                                user dashboard.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Step 3: Creating a Post (Sender) -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 3: Creating a Post (Sender)
                                        </h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>Navigate to Create Post:</b> Click on the "Create Post" button in
                                                your dashboard.</li>
                                            <li><b>Fill in the Parcel Details:</b> Provide information such as:</li>
                                            <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                                <li>Parcel Description</li>
                                                <li>Size and Weight</li>
                                                <li>Pickup Location</li>
                                                <li>Delivery Location</li>
                                                <li>Preferred Delivery Time</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <li><b>Set Payment Terms:</b> Indicate how much you are willing to pay the
                                                traveler.</li>
                                            <li><b>Publish Your Post:</b> Review the details and click "Post" to make it
                                                visible to travelers.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Step 4: Browsing and Approaching (Traveler) -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 4: Browsing and Approaching
                                            (Traveler)</h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>View Available Posts:</b> Go to the "Available Posts" section in your
                                                dashboard.</li>
                                            <li><b>Select a Parcel:</b> Browse through the listed parcels and click on
                                                one that interests you.</li>
                                            <li><b>Contact the Sender:</b> Use the "Contact" option to send a message or
                                                request more details.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Step 5: Agreement and Consent Form -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 5: Agreement and Consent
                                            Form</h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>Negotiate Terms:</b> Discuss the details, such as delivery time and
                                                payment, with the sender.</li>
                                            <li><b>Confirm Agreement:</b> Once both parties are satisfied, agree on the
                                                terms verbally or through the platform's messaging feature.</li>
                                            <li>
                                                <b>Fill Out the Consent Form:</b> Complete a digital consent form that
                                                outlines:
                                                <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                                                    <li>Delivery Details</li>
                                                    <li>Payment Agreement</li>
                                                    <li>Responsibilities of both parties</li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </li>
                                            <li><b>Submit the Form:</b> Ensure both parties sign and submit the consent
                                                form through the platform.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Step 6: Delivery Process -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 6: Delivery Process</h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>Pickup the Parcel:</b> The traveler picks up the parcel from the
                                                sender's specified location.</li>
                                            <li><b>Delivery:</b> The traveler delivers the parcel to the agreed
                                                destination.</li>
                                            <li><b>Complete Transaction:</b> After successful delivery, the sender
                                                confirms receipt, and the payment is processed.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Step 7: Feedback and Rating -->
                                    <div>
                                        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Step 7: Feedback and Rating</h2>
                                        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-gray-800">
                                            <li><b>Rate Your Experience:</b> After the transaction, both parties can
                                                rate each other and leave feedback.</li>
                                            <li><b>Improve the Community:</b> Use the feedback to enhance future
                                                interactions on the platform.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </main>

                            <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>